item.title: Need help
item.dc:creator: @Steph1 .Steph
item.description:
@Steph1 wrote:

Look on the thread, there should be the Hamachi Details. Copy them, (Name & Password).
Then go onto Hamachi and click on the Triangle > Join an existing Network > Add Details.

Thats Hamachi Done.

Then Open Moparscape and add the Server IP & Server Port.
Should be pretty straight foward from there? Make an Acc. and Log in

Thanks.
